    {
      "bookmarkId": "41477778_2_835-879",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "835-879",
      "markText": "对于帆船时期的海战，我们有着许多的经验性知识；而对于汽船时代的海战，我们却几乎一无所知。",
      "totalCount": 119,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41477778&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=835&rangeEnd=879",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27b328607278e69227b31df?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=835&rangeEnd=879"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41477778_2_2-56",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "2-56",
      "markText": "海权之历史，虽说绝非全部，却也在很大程度上，是一种对于国家间你争我斗、相互竞争以及以战争而告终之暴力的记述。",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41477778&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=2&rangeEnd=56",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27b328607278e69227b31df?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=2&rangeEnd=56"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41477778_1_363-388",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "363-388",
      "markText": "英格兰民族之伟大，比其他任何民族都更可归因于海洋。",
      "totalCount": 104,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41477778&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=363&rangeEnd=388",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27b328607278e69227b31df?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=363&rangeEnd=388"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41477778_3_3224-3295",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "3224-3295",
      "markText": "地处两大洋之间的美国，倘若东西沿海都有着大规模的海上贸易，那么它的地理位置要么会成为其海上力量极为薄弱的一个原因，要么就会让它付出高昂的代价。",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41477778&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3224&rangeEnd=3295",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27b328607278e69227b31df?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3224&rangeEnd=3295"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41477778_2_5876-5930",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "5876-5930",
      "markText": "武器的改良在于一两个人的力量，而战术上的改变则必须克服整个保守阶层的惰性才行；这种惰性，正是一种巨大的弊端。",
      "totalCount": 98,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41477778&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=5876&rangeEnd=5930",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27b328607278e69227b31df?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=5876&rangeEnd=5930"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41477778_2_118-205",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "118-205",
      "markText": "为了确保所属民族能够占有此种利益中超过其应得的份额，各国都会不遗余力地排斥其他国家，要么是通过和平的立法途径，用垄断或者禁止性条例，要么便是在立法途径失败之后，直接动用武力。",
      "totalCount": 88,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41477778&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=118&rangeEnd=205",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27b328607278e69227b31df?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=118&rangeEnd=205"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41477778_1_1467-1553",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "1467-1553",
      "markText": "所以本书之目标，便是将海洋利益推向前台，但又不将它们与普通历史的因果环境割裂开来，而是力图表明它们如何改变了普通历史的因果环境，以及它们是如何被普通历史的因果环境所改变的。",
      "totalCount": 84,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41477778&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=1467&rangeEnd=1553",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27b328607278e69227b31df?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=1467&rangeEnd=1553"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41477778_3_2808-2892",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2808-2892",
      "markText": "使得它既无需在陆地上捍卫自身，也不会受到诱惑，经由陆路去试图扩张自己的领土范围，那么，由于其目标一致针对的是海洋，所以它跟那些边境之一为陆地的民族相比，就具有了一种优势",
      "totalCount": 84,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41477778&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2808&rangeEnd=2892",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27b328607278e69227b31df?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2808&rangeEnd=2892"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41477778_3_5697-5753",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "5697-5753",
      "markText": "从贸易和军事角度来看，环境已使得地中海对世界历史所起的作用，比其他任何同等面积的水域对世界历史所起的作用都要大。",
      "totalCount": 75,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41477778&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5697&rangeEnd=5753",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27b328607278e69227b31df?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5697&rangeEnd=5753"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41477778_2_7616-7710",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "7616-7710",
      "markText": "在美国革命战争中，法国和西班牙在1779年结成了同盟，共同对抗英国。法、西联合舰队曾3次进击英吉利海峡，前线作战舰船一度达到了66艘；由于英军舰船数量远不及对方，所以英国舰队只得回港避战。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41477778&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=7616&rangeEnd=7710",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27b328607278e69227b31df?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=7616&rangeEnd=7710"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41477778_3_4107-4174",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "4107-4174",
      "markText": "地理位置上靠近敌人或攻击目标的这一优势，在哪里也没有在最近才得名的“贸易破坏战”这一战争形式中体现得更加明显；法国人称之为“游击战”。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41477778&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4107&rangeEnd=4174",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27b328607278e69227b31df?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4107&rangeEnd=4174"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41477778_3_21898-21981",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "21898-21981",
      "markText": "因此，虽说人民的勤劳和土地的多产并未让该国的商业贸易完全衰退下去，但人们都是带着一种羞耻感来从事贸易的，使得那些最有商业贸易才能的人一旦有可能，便纷纷离开了这一行业。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41477778&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=21898&rangeEnd=21981",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27b328607278e69227b31df?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=21898&rangeEnd=21981"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41477778_3_2-44",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2-44",
      "markText": "从政治和社会的观点来看，海洋首先并且最为明显地呈现给人们的就是，它是一条广袤的通途；",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41477778&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2&rangeEnd=44",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27b328607278e69227b31df?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2&rangeEnd=44"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41477778_3_8417-8456",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "8417-8456",
      "markText": "大自然赐予英国的东西却很少，直到制造业发展起来之前，英国都没有什么东西可供出口",
